A Solutions Architect is reviewing IAM policies and finds the following policy attached to an EC2 instance role:
{
  "Effect": "Allow",
  "Action": "s3:*",
  "Resource": "*",
  "Condition": {
    "StringEquals": {
      "s3:prefix": ["finance/", "hr/"]
    }
  }
}
The instance attempts to call s3:ListBucket on a bucket named 'company-data'. Will the call succeed?
